        {
            "title": "「大錯特錯」 英國首相施紀賢反對特朗普加徵歐洲國家關稅",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 英國首相施紀賢對美國總統<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:特朗普;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/特朗普\">特朗普</a>威脅對歐洲國家加徵新關稅的行為表明立場，稱此舉將損害英國經濟。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在周一上午針對特朗普周末宣布加徵關稅而召開的記者會上，他強調，「對盟友實施關稅是完全錯誤的。貿易戰不符合任何一方利益。」他警告稱，「此類措施將損害英國工人、英國企業和英國經濟。」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"觀看：斯塔默稱特朗普的新關稅威脅「完全錯誤」，並表示「貿易戰不符合任何一方的利益」。Source: Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gGNozMf_7fd980ciQBSSHg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/a86a34d4cfb14650219c152ce265eede\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">觀看：斯塔默稱特朗普的新關稅威脅「完全錯誤」，並表示「貿易戰不符合任何一方的利益」。Source: Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">斯塔默就特朗普對格陵蘭島的主張重申了對丹麥的支持立場。「這涉及一項不可動搖的原則，因為它關乎穩定可信的國際合作如何運作，」他表示。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5e21400b-e6ba-3c45-bae2-a19d0bd3dae5-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">斯塔默於周日下午與特朗普了電話，此前已分別與丹麥首相梅特·弗雷澤裡克森、歐盟委員會主席烏爾蘇拉·馮德萊恩以及北約秘書長馬克·呂特進行了通話。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">特朗普周六在社交媒體Truth Social上宣布，將從2月1日起對包括英國在內的在格陵蘭問題上站到丹麥一邊的歐洲八國加徵10%的關稅。他威脅稱將從6月起把稅率提高至25%，除非並直至「就全面、徹底購買格陵蘭達成協議」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Starmer Rebukes Trump Threats as ‘Completely Wrong’ From an Ally</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A7%E9%8C%AF%E7%89%B9%E9%8C%AF-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E9%A6%96%E7%9B%B8%E6%96%AF%E5%A1%94%E9%BB%98%E5%B0%8D%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%A0%E5%BE%B5%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85%E4%BA%AE%E6%98%8E%E7%AB%8B%E5%A0%B4-102236061.html",
